Gambia will be hoping to utilize their home advantage to claim all three points, while Ivory Coast will be looking to put up a strong challenge to claim the victory on the road.
The match is expected to be a fiercely contested battle as both teams will be looking to secure a vital win to boost their position in the league standings.
